data.title: National Symbols of Afghanistan
data.meta_description: A description of the national symbols of Afghanistan.
data.text:
This land is Afghanistan,

It is the pride of every Afghan

The land of peace, the land of sword,

Each of its sons is brave

This land will shine for ever,

like the sun in the blue sky

In the chest of Asia,

It will remain as heart forever

We will follow the one God

We all say, "Allah is the greatest!",

we all say, "Allah is the greatest!",

We all say, "Allah is the greatest!"
